{"tid":997003,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"再見亦是朋友？","createTime":"2019-01-26T18:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T18:27:49.000Z","uid":72915,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7d2e0b6555553eb9c398062b05f772a8caadc4ae","tid":997003,"uid":72915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T18:16:32.000Z","msg":"同女朋友分左手大約一個月，原因係因為工作冷淡左，而佢有追求姐，從而且想嘗試下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nEx只係第一次拍拖，而我拍過幾次，結果一齊左4年。<br />\n經歷過dse同大專，當我做野開始好少理佢，又冇乜理佢感受。一直忍，結果因為一次嘈交而講分手。<br />\n我有追番佢,唔知佢感動定內疚，分手後照樣有出幾日街但最尾做番sweet野都喊，最後發現原來佢係鍾意左第二個。<br />\n佢一直想話做番普通朋友/家人咁，但我睇唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實佢都有新戀情，乜真係咁缺朋友咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外，其實我好想等佢，始終佢只係第一次拍拖，比佢嘗試下都好<br />\n點先可以追番佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d034acc231ab2bd72bbea30919f663fac382abe1","tid":997003,"uid":184932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T18:24:01.000Z","msg":"86cm 咁長 <br />\n條女唔鍾意<br />\n<br />\nsp都做唔到"},{"pid":"88e56856fb8221f05a5ebf32b8c10ce516a3221d","tid":997003,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T18:24:40.000Z","msg":"正所謂掟煲唔掟蓋"},{"pid":"5731e7b019039d257e34aa80c2f0efa05409ba55","tid":997003,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T18:24:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1aec162a83327d0c1aab9304ff27f045e1ff46","tid":997003,"uid":404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T18:27:49.000Z","msg":"你而家係典型香港分手後日記<br />\n<br />\n過來人提你一句<br />\n你同佢會糾纏可能一年半載<br />\n但若一年後，你同佢朋友都不再係<br />\n佢所謂習慣你的習慣 都可以用時間消逝盡<br />\n<br />\n若干年後 如果佢單身，你單身 喧寒問暖一下<br />\n有緣你仲有一絲機會追得返佢 但已經唔係當初你懷念的她"}]}